Prerequisite:
1. python >= 2.7
2. lxml
3. scrapy http://charlesmartinreid.com/wiki/Scrapy


Install:
--ubuntu--
* sudo apt-get install libxml2-dev libxslt-dev python-dev python-pip
* pip install lxml
* sudo apt-get install python-scrapy

--centos--
* sudo yum install libxml2-devel libxslt-devel python-devel python-pip
* pip install lxml
* sudo yum install python-scrapy

Run:
* create a tutorial project
	scrapy startproject tutorial
* test with tutorial
	scrapy crawl dmoz

Run with appinfo:
enter the root directory of appinfo and run with:
* test:
scrapy crawl appinfo
* run:
scrapy crawl appinfo -t csv -o app.csv -a filename=appid.list

appid.list: file contains a list of appid to scrapy from google play
app.csv: result file with csv format



